Xiao Cui,

869
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,250
don't you like singing?

870
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,880
Sing us a couple of songs.

871
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,260
After you sing,

872
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:11,680
write a self-criticism,

873
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:13,280
and we'll let this matter go.

874
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:15,600
Sing.

875
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:18,600
Come on, sing.

876
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:19,920
Sing now.

877
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:22,250
When I tell you to sing, you'd better sing.

878
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:29,960
Alright.

879
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,000
The next song

880
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:35,080
is dedicated to our dear factory director.

881
00:38:35,120 --> 00:38:36,560
I hope your life

882
00:38:37,200 --> 00:38:38,400
every day

883
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:40,360
will be as happy

884
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:42,320
as these lyrics.

885
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,080
Okay.

886
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:46,120
Thank you.

887
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:47,920
Thank you.

888
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:05,760
Iron doors, iron windows, iron chains.

889
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:11,360
Hands gripping the iron bars, looking out.

890
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:12,440
Cui Guoming, what do you mean?

891
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,200
Get out!

892
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,040
Cui Guoming!

893
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:16,280
What kind of place do you think this is?

894
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:18,010
You think you can act wild here?

895
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:20,960
You're suspended pending investigation.

896
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:23,680
This is outrageous!

897
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,160
He hit me!

898
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:27,600
My uncle and the factory director had an unfortunate misunderstanding.

899
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,760
The misunderstanding between both sides grew deeper and deeper.

900
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:30,920
From this moment on,

901
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:33,960
Uncle completely set his life free.

902
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,200
He never imagined

903
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:38,000
how brilliant and colorful his life would become.

904
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,200
Happy.

905
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,160
Satisfying.

906
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:45,960
How could I bow down to the powerful,

907
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:48,560
and lose my joyful expression?

908
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:49,960
That's right!

909
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:51,360
Beat him up!

910
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,320
Well done!

911
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:55,600
I really can't stay here anymore.

912
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:56,680
I can't take this humiliation.

913
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:58,160
I don't even care if they fire me.

914
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:58,880
That's right.

915
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,680
If you quit, what will you do?

916
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:01,320
Where would you go?

917
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,440
You'll have nothing to eat.

918
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,040
You have a family to support.

919
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:05,600
Heaven won't let a sparrow starve,

920
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:07,120
so it won't let me starve either.

921
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:07,960
That's right.

922
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:10,600
Why are you joining in?

923
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:16,480
Iron doors, iron windows, iron chains.

924
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:23,000
Hands holding the iron bars, looking outside.

925
00:40:23,160 --> 00:40:27,680
How beautiful the outside world is!

926
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,600
Can you stop singing?

927
00:40:31,720 --> 00:40:33,520
Keep singing and I'll knock your teeth out.

928
00:40:33,520 --> 00:40:35,650
Does your family own this restaurant?

929
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:39,240
Where did this wild beast come from?

930
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:42,330
Let's settle this with a fight.

931
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,800
What did you just say?

932
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,560
I said let's have a little fight.

933
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,160
Not that one.

934
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:20,960
The one before.

935
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:22,420
Is this restaurant yours?

936
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:23,730
The one before that.

937
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:25,220
What did I say earlier?

938
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:28,640
Could you keep it down?

939
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:30,840
Believe me, I'll break your teeth if you keep singing.

940
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:31,640
I believe you.

941
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:33,960
I believe you.

942
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:37,080
How could you not believe me?

943
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:38,200
I can't.

944
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,640
I don't believe you.

945
00:41:39,640 --> 00:41:40,760
Won't you just beat me up?

946
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,200
No, that's not right.

947
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:43,800
You should say you don't believe me.

948
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:44,240
Right?

949
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:44,840
If you say you don't believe me,

950
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,360
then I can smack you.

951
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:47,120
Only then can I hit you.

952
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:48,280
Now you say you believe me,

953
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,120
so now I'm just...

954
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:50,160
I can't do it.

955
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:50,960
What am I supposed to do?

956
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:51,320
Right, now I...

957
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,760
I just don't want you to hit me.

958
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,000
That won't work.

959
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:54,720
I have to hit you, brother.

960
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,560
Why?

961
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:56,280
Recently...

962
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,560
I just got out of prison.

963
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,840
I just got released.

964
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,560
My brothers said,

965
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:01,280
'Big brother, let's go get some food,

966
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:01,960
have some drinks,

967
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,440
get some barbecue and stuff.'

968
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,960
I had just sat down,

969
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:07,360
and you started singing about iron bars and prison cells.

970
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,920
You made me sad.

971
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:09,880
I'm sorry,

972
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:10,680
big brother.

973
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:11,680
I am...

974
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:12,080
I'm sorry.

975
00:42:12,080 --> 00:42:12,560
I am...

976
00:42:15,200 --> 00:42:17,720
Isn't this guy quite polite?

977
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,200
Uncle!

978
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:21,240
Uncle!

979
00:42:21,720 --> 00:42:22,760
Come out for a second!

980
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,360
Hurry!

981
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:26,080
You even brought a kid.

982
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:27,920
You're just hanging around here with nothing better to do.

983
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:30,120
What kind of person are you?

984
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:30,480
Come on, big brother.

985
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:31,480
I'm just visiting.

986
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:33,160
Brother, do you believe me?

987
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,280
No.

988
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:35,600
Yes, yes!

989
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:36,280
What am I doing? What?

990
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,880
I don't know what you're talking about believing or not.

991
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:38,880
I'm just visiting.

992
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,210
What's wrong, Xiaoxue?

993
00:42:40,720 --> 00:42:41,720
Mr. Cui,

994
00:42:42,120 --> 00:42:44,160
my father has been arrested.

995
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,800
W-what happened?

996
00:42:49,720 --> 00:42:51,650
The police station just called me.

997
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:55,120
They said my father is a murderer.

998
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:56,960
It's okay.
